Suspected Islamic Militant Gunmen Shoot Policeman in Maiduguri in Nigeria

-- B y   A r d o   H a z z a d
-- 
2011-05-06T06:27:04Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-06/suspected-islamic-militant-gunmen-shoot-policeman-in-maiduguri-in-nigeria.html
Gunmen in  Nigeria  suspected to be
Islamic militants shot dead a policeman and injured another
yesterday in the northeastern city of Maiduguri, police said.   “We believe it is the work of members of Boko Haram,” Mai
Mamman, police spokesman in the city said by phone today,
referring to a radical Islamic sect that draws inspiration from
 Afghanistan ’s Taliban movement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ardo Hazzad in Bauchi at 
 ahazzad@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
